{"action":"send","to":"qa","taskId":"demo-delegate-1","type":"review_request","message":"Hi QA, I've completed the debounce utility. Here's the implementation:

```javascript
function debounce(fn, delay, options = {}) {
  let timerId;
  const { leading = false, trailing = true } = options;

  return function(...args) {
    const isLeading = leading && !timerId;

    clearTimeout(timerId);

    if (isLeading) {
      fn.apply(this, args);
    }

    timerId = setTimeout(() => {
      if (trailing && !isLeading) {
        fn.apply(this, args);
      }
      timerId = null;
    }, delay);
  };
}
```

Could you please review edge cases? Especially the leading+trailing combination."}

